---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Base title="Error">
  <section class="flex flex-col h-[100dvh] max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-16">

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-7xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 text-left">
        Sorry, you have been blocked
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-muted text-left">
        You are unable to access the website at this time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:space-x-12 space-y-8 md:space-y-0">
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">What Happened?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Your access to this website has been restricted. This may occur for various reasons, such as suspicious automated traffic, malicious activity, actions that triggered a block, access from a restricted country, or exceeding allowed request rates. These measures are in place to ensure the security and availability of the site.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">What Can I Do?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Please try disabling any VPNs, proxies, or automated scripts that might be affecting your connection. Ensure your browser is up to date and that no unusual extensions or network tools are interfering. If you believe your access has been restricted in error, contact the website administrator and provide the request ID below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-sm text-muted space-y-1">
      <div>Request ID: %REQUEST_ID% · %REQUEST_TIMESTAMP% UTC</div>
      <div>
        <span class="ml-4">
          Proxy by <a href="https://vaneproxy.com" class="text-muted">Vane v%VANE_VERSION%</a>
        </span>
        <span class="cursor-pointer" onclick="this.textContent='Request IP: %REQUEST_IP%';">
          · Request IP: Click to reveal
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Base>
